3) All Beauty - This category encompasses all beauty products, including skincare items like sheet masks.

4) Luxury Beauty - Depending on the brand and price point of the sheet mask, it could be classified as a luxury beauty product.

5) Skin Care - This category specifically focuses on skincare products, and the sheet mask falls under this category as it is used for moisturizing and brightening the skin.
